title: Captain America/Black Panther - Flags Of Our Fathers (2010|DCP)
description:
Promotional info - "For the first time ever, see the full story of the first meeting of Captain America and the Black Panther! It's a World War II adventure featuring a young Steve Rogers, the Black Panther and Nick Fury and his Howling Commandos in combat with the nastiest Nazi villains in the Marvel Universe!"

This great limited series is written by Reginald Hudlin with art by Denys Cowan. There are a few different copies of the individual issues out there; after checking them all out, these 2013 Bchry-DCP scans are the best IMHO. Thanks to that group for their usual excellent work; please seed and enjoy! :-)
